1
00:00:02,087 --> 00:00:04,756
<i>- Previously:</i>
- You're to be congratulated.

2
00:00:04,840 --> 00:00:09,887
Your son is now the proud owner
of River Run.

3
00:00:09,970 --> 00:00:13,182
I can procure you whatever you wish.
I know an Irish seafaring gentlemen

4
00:00:13,265 --> 00:00:14,808
who does business in Wilmington.

5
00:00:14,892 --> 00:00:16,560
My husband's whisky venture...

6
00:00:16,643 --> 00:00:19,563
Mr Bonnet doesn't do business
with people he doesn't know.

7
00:00:19,646 --> 00:00:22,983
Mr Bonnet will be personally meeting
Mr Alexander Malcolm.

8
00:00:23,066 --> 00:00:24,443
You must kill Stephen Bonnet.

9
00:00:24,526 --> 00:00:26,361
Don't know
if I can take another man's life.

10
00:00:26,445 --> 00:00:29,823
A plan has been put in motion
to find and kill Stephen Bonnet.

11
00:00:29,907 --> 00:00:32,367
Bonnet could have the right
to take Jemmy away from us.

12
00:00:32,451 --> 00:00:33,493
He attacked me.

13
00:00:33,577 --> 00:00:37,080
People of this time see the child as proof
that you were a willing participant.

14
00:00:37,164 --> 00:00:38,916
I could've been brave. I could've fought.

15
00:00:38,999 --> 00:00:40,584
I hate myself for what happened.

16
00:00:40,667 --> 00:00:43,086
- You couldn't have stopped him.
- I could have tried harder.

17
00:00:43,170 --> 00:00:44,421
It took courage not to fight.

18
00:00:44,504 --> 00:00:46,715
If ye did, he would have killed ye.

